translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_939f79ac:
    # "{i}Susan?.. My psychologist?… Or rather, my former psychologist!{/i}"
    "{i}Susan?.. Psikologku?... Atau lebih tepatnya, mantan psikologku!{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_cd1773b1:
    # "{i}Of course, it's her. Who else would stand out so dramatically among everyone else?{/i}"
    "{i}Tentu saja itu dia. Siapa lagi yang bisa terlihat begitu mencolok di antara semua orang?{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_dd5821b5:
    # "{i}She's showing off.{/i}"
    "{i}Dia sedang pamer.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_986ab52b:
    # "{i}And she's damn good at it.{/i}"
    "{i}Dan dia sangat hebat dalam hal itu.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_69c89e36:
    # "{i}So, the vacation voucher to 'Bounty' was her doing.{/i}"
    "{i}Jadi, voucher liburan ke 'Bounty' itu perbuatannya.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_89aabf62:
    # "{i}But why?.. What's with this generosity?{/i}"
    "{i}Tapi kenapa?.. Ada apa dengan kemurahan hati ini?{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_3e15225a:
    # "{i}Obviously, she expects me to swim over and ask her myself.{/i}"
    "{i}Jelas, dia berharap aku berenang ke sana dan menanyakannya sendiri.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_557dce02:
    # "{i}Am I on the hook again?{/i}"
    "{i}Apa aku terpancing lagi?{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_07fef605:
    # "{i}To hell with her!{/i}"
    "{i}Persetan dengannya!{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_ff09c475:
    # "{i}I could just stay on the beach out of spite.{/i}"
    "{i}Aku bisa saja tetap di pantai hanya untuk membuatnya kesal.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_b3717bf0:
    # "{i}After all, why should I care about her?{/i}"
    "{i}Lagi pula, kenapa aku harus peduli padanya?{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_1dc8c196:
    # "{i}If she wants to see me, she can swim over here herself.{/i}"
    "{i}Kalau dia ingin menemuiku, dia bisa berenang ke sini sendiri.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_e49429b9:
    # "{i}.....{/i}"
    "{i}.....{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_445c009b:
    # "{i}Or not?..{/i}"
    "{i}Atau tidak?..{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_f527eeff:
    # "{i}She's toying with me again… That damn woman makes me think about her. Dream about her…{/i}"
    "{i}Dia mempermainkanku lagi... Wanita sialan itu membuatku memikirkannya. Memimpikannya...{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_4d08bb7b:
    # "{i}Want her...{/i}"
    "{i}Menginginkannya...{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_29a62063:
    # "{i}Okay, stop!!! I decide when and who I fantasize about.{/i}"
    "{i}Oke, berhenti!!! Aku yang menentukan kapan dan siapa yang kufantasikan.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_55929295:
    # "{i}One way or another, if I want to figure out her motives, either she has to come ashore, or I have to get closer.{/i}"
    "{i}Bagaimanapun, kalau aku ingin memahami motifnya, entah dia harus naik ke pantai, atau aku harus mendekat.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_c50b2fd3:
    # "{i}Except I can't swim…{/i}"
    "{i}Masalahnya aku tidak bisa berenang...{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_e791d0a4:
    # "{i}A swimming ring would come in handy right about now.{/i}"
    "{i}Pelampung renang akan sangat berguna sekarang.{/i}"

translate indonesian beatch_seria_sus_1_eb79df03:
    # "{i}Yeah, by the way, where do I get one?{/i}"
    "{i}Ya, ngomong-ngomong, di mana aku bisa mendapatkannya?{/i}"
